data.description: Imagine a home that is warm, welcoming, filled with light, high ceilings and tall windows, all in Midway ISD. That's what you'll find here, along with 4 bedrooms, 2 and half bathrooms, an elegant formal dining or sitting room, and so many more custom home features such as a gas fireplace, beautiful built ins, smart home system, and surround sound. The well appointed kitchen is open in concept while still providing plenty of custom, wood cabinet storage and ample granite counter space. This home is also wired for an emergency generator in the event of crazy Texas weather. The backyard is ready for outdoor fun, with half being grass and half a sprawling, smooth, concrete surface that is perfect for outdoor play, or even your next pickle ball or basketball game. Come and see what 1413 Fossil Ridge has to offer!
